<section id="contact" class="bg-gray-900/50 py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4">¿Quieres formar parte de nuestra comunidad?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">
            Únete a Clean Cod3 y conecta con otros desarrolladores, participa en eventos y contribuye a proyectos
            open source. Estamos siempre buscando nuevos miembros apasionados por el código limpio.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <button class="glow-button inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white shadow transition-colors hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-gray-900">
              Unirse ahora
            </button>
            <button class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-gray-600 bg-transparent px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white shadow-sm transition-colors hover:bg-gray-800 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-gray-900">
              Contáctanos
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-900/30 border border-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-4">Suscríbete a nuestro newsletter</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">
            Recibe actualizaciones sobre eventos, recursos y oportunidades para desarrolladores.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="grid w-full items-center gap-1.5">
              <label for="email" class="text-sm font-medium">
                Email
              </label>
              <input
                type="email"
                id="email"
                placeholder="tu@email.com"
                class="flex h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-gray-700 bg-gray-950 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-gray-900"
              />
            </div>
            <button class="w-full inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow transition-colors hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-gray-900">
              Suscribirse
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <style>
    .glow-button {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .glow-button::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5);
      filter: blur(20px);
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
      z-index: -1;
      transform: scale(1.05);
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    
    .glow-button:hover::before {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  </style>
  
  